title: #92Noon! Flatter/JonK/Leber/Wobby/TwinsColdCall
description: VSIN's Ron Flatter opens the show with Kentucky Derby opinions, Jonny Athletic on the hiring of Gersson Rosas as new POBO for the Wolves, Leber in studio midway through, Wobby with film breakdowns on Vikings rookies, plus a cool Twins cold-call featuring Byron Buxton!
